summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 234W. page 30, of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Acre 1, Block 23, Maple Leaf Addition to Green Lake Circle, from RS 5000 to RM 800 contingent upon the recording of a properly executed, delivered and accepted Property Use and Development Agreement pertaining to such property (Petition of Russell Nelson, C.F. 284097, Hearing Examiner No. X-76-282).
